<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to <%= title %></h1>
    <p>This is a CRUD API server with JWT authentication and MongoDB.</p>
    <h2>Available Endpoints:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>POST /users - Register new user</li>
        <li>POST /login - Login user</li>
        <li>GET /users - Get all users (admin only)</li>
        <li>GET /users/:id - Get single user</li>
        <li>PUT /users/:id - Update user</li>
        <li>DELETE /users/:id - Delete user</li>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>